[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "世界中に散らばっていた９枚の「九偉人図」……\nぶっちゃけ、見つけられるのか半信半疑だったけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00889",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "今、こうして全部がここにある……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00890",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "それじゃ、「九偉人図」を全部\nくっつけてみるね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00891",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "えーっと、ここと、ここが繋がるのかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00892",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "なんだか謎解きみたい！\nいったいどんな真実が隠されているのかな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00893",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "できた！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00894",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "わ、なんだろうこれ……\nそれぞれ違う模様の丸が、９個描いてある……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00895",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "裏には薄っすらと、９人の人が描いてあるわ……\nなんか、見たことあるような……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00896",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "９……九偉人を指しているのかしら",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00897",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "繋がった情報は……星の配置を表しているみたい。\n暗黒の氷海の、この配置で星が見える場所に――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00898",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "そこに、果ての大陸がある……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00899",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ついに！　果ての大陸の場所が分かるのね……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00900",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "おぉ……！　それは嬉しいけど、\n結局、暗黒の氷海は避けられないのかぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_00901",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うお～……。マジっすか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00902",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "メーヴェ",
		"romanized_name": "Mowen",
		"model_path_hash": "8282561094361780418",
		"text": "まあまあ、腹を括るしかないならないで、\nお姉さん頑張っちゃうわよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_235_037_00903",
		"still_path_hash": "7917604627487944706",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ま、待ってね！　まだ何か書いてあるよ。\nこれは古い文字だから、えーっと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00904",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "「九人の偉人、皆がその手を差し伸べしとき\n　汝が前に、果てへの道は開かれん」",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00905",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "読めるの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_037_00906",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "これでも英才教育を受けてきた身だから。\nえっへん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00907",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "「九人の偉人」って、もしかしなくても九偉人よね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00908",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "シトリンたちが力を貸してくれたら、\nいけるってことだろうけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00909",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "ヘルトと、ゼロも……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00910",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あの二人が力を貸すってのは、\nあんまり想像できないわね……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00911",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ええっと、二人の身柄は今\nランターナのほうで預かってるんでしたよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00912",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "うん、そうだよ。\nでもちょっと、ヘルトのほうの様子がおかしくて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00913",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ヘルトが……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00914",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "なんだか、魂が抜けた～、みたいな。\nなんにもやる気がない、関心がないって感じなんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00915",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "まあなんにせよ、協力を依頼するなら\nとりあえずここまで二人を連れて来るね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_037_00916",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "はい、お願いします！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_037_00917",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "いよいよ……あの最果てにもう１回、\n挑戦する時が近づいてきた、か",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00918",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]